class GraphADT:
    def __init__(self):
        self.vertices = {}

    def add_vertex(self, v):
        if v not in self.vertices:
            self.vertices[v] = set()

    def add_edge(self, u, v):
        self.add_vertex(u)
        self.add_vertex(v)
        self.vertices[u].add(v)
        self.vertices[v].add(u)

    def degree(self, v):
        return len(self.vertices.get(v, set()))

    def neighbors(self, v):
        return self.vertices.get(v, set())
```

复杂度：
- `add_vertex`/`add_edge`：O(1) 摊销
- `degree`/`neighbors`：O(1)

